dev.efnilite.witp.generator

Class ParkourGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.efnilite.witp.generator.DefaultGenerator

  • public class ParkourGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    The class that generates the parkour, which each ParkourPlayer has.
    Important notice: tempering with details in this class could result in complete malfunction of code since this class has been meticulously made using a lot of cross-references. Same goes for SubareaDivider.
    Author:
    Efnilite

        public void generateNext()
        Generates the next parkour block, choosing between structures and normal jumps. If it's a normal jump, it will get a random distance between them and whether it goes up or not. Note: please be cautious when messing about with parkour generation, since even simple changes could break the entire plugin
